ition for pollination among coexisting Burmeistera.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Muchhala, Nathan", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/de4a1feaaa8c779b5a49df4484694bf7", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/d87ae372847bae999468db0059e74d0d92e9654de60cc1718ebd35633e41c948", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/3DAQNJ2N", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/3DAQNJ2N", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/1d0efdde9dc1de823ef5d19593ae4f18!/b169164-171888", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "3", "pages": "332-337", "title": "Biotropica", "volume": "40"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/de4a1feaaa8c779b5a49df4484694bf7"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:3DAQNJ2N"}, {"identifier": "10.1111/j.1744-7429.2007.00381.x"}], "communities": [{"id": "biosyslit"}, {"id": "batlit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "13511438"}}]}}, "title": "Functional Significance of Interspecific Variation in Burmeistera Flower Morphology: Evidence from Nectar Bat Captures in Ecuador", "links": {"self": "https://zenodo.org/api/records/13511439", 